Given the clear, direct wording of the resolution and the matching data, my confidence is high. The old "Phường Tích Lương" is now part of the new "Phường Tích Lương" with code "05500" within the unchanged "Tỉnh Thái Nguyên."  My output will accurately reflect this transformation, with the relevant citation from the resolution for full transparency. This is a pretty straightforward case of ward reorganization.
